h17 yb4 ff2 fs9 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">The marital life of the prophet, described in the first three chapters, </div><div class="t md3 x42 h17 yb5 ff2 fs9 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">served as a graphic illustration of how faithless Israel was breaking the heart </div><div class="t md4 x42 h17 yb6 ff2 fs9 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">of her heavenly Husband. </div><div class="t md5 xd h17 yb7 ff2 fs9 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">The rest of the book contains strong denunciations against the unfaithful-</div><div class="t md6 x32 h17 yb8 ff2 fs9 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">ness of God&apos;s chosen people. Assurances of God&apos;s love are mixed with </div><div class="t md7 x32 h17 yb9 ff2 fs9 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">promises of mercy. If the Israelites will turn from their evil ways God will </div><div class="t md8 x32 h17 yba ff2 fs9 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">accept them gladly. </div><div class="t md9 x33 h17 ybb ff2 fs9 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">Although written many centuries ago, the book of Hosea contains much </div><div class="t mda x32 h17 ybc ff2 fs9 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">that is present truth today. It deserves careful and prayerful study. </div><div class="t mdb xc h10 y3d ff1 fs9 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">OVERVIEW OF THE BOOK OF HOSEA </div><div class="t mdc x43 h10 ybd ff1 fs9 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">Hosea 1— 4 </div><div class="t mdd x44 h10 ybd ff1 fs9 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">Hosea 4 —13 </div><div class="t mde x11 h10 ybe ff1 fs9 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">Hosea 14 </div><div class="t mdf x2e h10 ybf ff1 fs9 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">Hosea&apos;s unhappy </div><div class="t me0 x8 h10 yc0 ff1 fs9 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">marriage—a </div><div class="t me1 x8 h10 yc1 ff1 fs9 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">warning of Israel&apos;s </div><div class="t me2 x8 h10 yc2 ff1 fs9 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">spiritual apostasy </div><div class="t me3 x3b h10 yc3 ff1 fs9 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">A warning of </div><div class="t mcf x36 h10 yc4 ff1 fs9 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">judgment mixed </div><div class="t me4 x36 h10 yc1 ff1 fs9 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">with God&apos;s </div><div class="t me5 x36 h10 yc2 ff1 fs9 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">appeals </div><div class="t me6 x29 h10 yc5 ff1 fs9 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">Appeal for Israel to </div><div class="t me7 x45 h10 yc6 ff1 fs9 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">repent in order </div><div class="t me8 x45 h10 yc7 ff1 fs9 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">that God&apos;s plan for </div><div class="t me9 x45 h10 yc8 ff1 fs9 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">Israel can be put </div><div class="t mea x45 h10 yc9 ff1 fs9 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">into effect </div></div><div class="pi" data-data='{"ctm":[1.000000,0.000000,0.000000,1.000000,0.000000,0.000000]}'></div></div>
